                p You can assign tasks to board members.
              div.span6.help-img
            section.row-fluid
              div.span6.help-img
              div.span6
                h2 View your notifications.
                p You can view your notifications such as tasks assigned to you, invitations to join     oards and so on.
            section.row-fluid
              div.span6
